Description: GStreamer debugging and monitoring tracers plugin
 GStreamer plugin providing various debugging and monitoring tracers.
 This plugin contains:
  - buffer_lateness: Track buffer lateness in pipelines
  - queue_levels: Monitor queue fill levels
  - pad_push_timings: Measure pad push operation timings
  - pcap_writer: Capture pipeline data in PCAP format
  - pipeline_snapshot: Generate pipeline state snapshots (Unix only)
  - memory_tracer: Track memory usage (requires GStreamer >= 1.26)
 .
 These tracers are useful for debugging, profiling, and monitoring
 GStreamer pipelines in development and production environments.